keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

unmap f
unmap d
unmap x
unmap m
unmap v
unmap /
unmap o
unmap b
unmap p
unmap n
unmap N
unmap `
unmap <c-e>
map m Mute or unmute current tab
unmap H
unmap yf
unmap <a-f>
unmap z
unmap zH
unmap zL
map h previousTab
map l nextTab
map L scrollRight
map H scrollLeft
map r reload
map gd LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink
map i LinkHints.activateMode
map I LinkHints.activateModeToOpenIncognito
map : LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map * LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue

map p openCopiedUrlInNewTab
map P openCopiedUrlInCurrentTab

map f scrollPageDown
map d scrollPageUp
map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map u goBack
map <c-r> goForward

map <c-[> passNextKey
map <c-]> passNextKey
